<section class="suds-stack">
  <div class="suds-stack__wrap">
    <div class="suds-stack__intro">
      <p class="suds-stack__eyebrow">How booking works</p>
      <h2>A cleaner booking process from quote to appointment.</h2>
      <p>
        Suds Auto Salon quotes based on vehicle size, condition, location, and the result you want.
        That keeps the recommendation accurate and helps make sure the right amount of time is reserved.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-stack__steps">
      <article>
        <span>1</span>
        <h3>Share the vehicle</h3>
        <p>Send the vehicle year, make, model, city, and a few interior/exterior photos if possible.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>2</span>
        <h3>Get matched</h3>
        <p>Sam recommends Basic, Signature, Elite Reset, Ceramic, or maintenance based on condition and goals.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <span>3</span>
        <h3>Get it handled</h3>
        <p>The detail is performed at your home, office, apartment, or approved mobile service location.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-stack__split">
      <div>
        <p class="suds-stack__eyebrow">Add only what matters</p>
        <h2>Upgrade for the problems your car actually has.</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Pet hair:</strong> for embedded hair and heavy debris.</li>
          <li><strong>Stain extraction:</strong> for seats, carpets, mats, and family vehicle spills.</li>
          <li><strong>Odor treatment:</strong> for lingering cabin smell after the clean.</li>
          <li><strong>Paint enhancement:</strong> for more gloss and cleaner reflections.</li>
          <li><strong>Ceramic protection:</strong> for easier washing and longer-term paint defense.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="suds-stack__quote">
        <h3>Best value path</h3>
        <p><strong>First:</strong> Signature Detail or Elite Reset.</p>
        <p><strong>Then:</strong> exterior protection or paint enhancement.</p>
        <p><strong>After:</strong> monthly maintenance plan.</p>
        <a href="/pages/contact-us">Request a Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-stack__reviews">
      <article>
        <p>"He came to my house with all that he needed. Highly recommend Sam and Suds Auto Salon."</p>
        <strong>Stacy K. - Edmonds, WA</strong>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p>"He got old stains out of the seats and thoroughly cleaned every nook and cranny."</p>
        <strong>Dane U. - Seattle, WA</strong>
      </article>
      <article>
        <p>"My car interior was done with great detail, it looks better than when I got it at the dealer."</p>
        <strong>Alinafe M. - Lake Forest Park, WA</strong>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-stack {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111111;
  }

  .suds-stack__wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 20px;
  }

  .suds-stack__intro {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .suds-stack__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #8c6b05;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .suds-stack h2 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-stack h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-stack p,
  .suds-stack li {
    color: #292929;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .suds-stack__steps,
  .suds-stack__reviews {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 34px;
  }

  .suds-stack__steps article,
  .suds-stack__reviews article,
  .suds-stack__split,
  .suds-stack__quote {
    border: 1px solid #dedede;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #f7f7f7;
  }

  .suds-stack__steps span {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #111111;
    color: #f2d36b;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .suds-stack__split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.35fr) minmax(280px, .65fr);
    gap: 22px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 44px;
  }

  .suds-stack__split ul {
    margin: 18px 0 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .suds-stack__quote {
    background: #fffaf0;
    border-color: #b9931b;
  }

  .suds-stack__quote a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #111111;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .suds-stack__reviews strong {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: #111111;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    .suds-stack__steps,
    .suds-stack__reviews,
    .suds-stack__split {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .suds-stack__wrap {
      padding: 44px 18px;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Suds revenue stack",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Suds revenue stack"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
